name: Quarter Up Bar Arcade
description:
Fun Bar with typical bar food menu.  Modern Games $1, older games 50 cents.  Both sterns are insider connected.  Good drink prices. Change machine.

Pinball machines kept in very good working order. Minor issues, but flippers all work and with power.
Nice selection. Rotated somewhat often.
Many premium Stern games (not just Pro like so many places)
Staff very friendly and stayed open later than posted closing time ‚Äúbecause people were still playing games.‚Äù
